    "The project's goal was to create a tool for better pesticide handling by diagnosing and categorizing plant diseases using contemporary technology and simple internet connectivity Singh et al. (2020).",
    "Additionally, a thorough investigation and research on the identification and classification of plant leaves using CNN were provided.",
